### 0. DEV-ONLY: Mock Login (Bypass Firebase untuk Testing Lokal)
# PINTASAN TESTING: Masukkan email admin/user di database Anda.
# Endpoint ini hanya aktif dalam mode debug/development (gin.Mode() == gin.DebugMode).
# Anda tidak perlu mempunyai Firebase Google ID token untuk skenario ini!
# Salin access_token dari respons di bawah, lalu tempel ke variabel @token di baris 43.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/v1/dev-login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gerai.org"
}

###

### 1. Login Admin/User (Menggunakan Fitur Autentikasi Tim Anda - Firebase ID Token)
# Anda memerlukan Firebase Google ID Token (token_id) hasil login di sisi Frontend.
# Kirim token_id ini sebagai Form-urlencoded atau Form-data.
# Jika berhasil, ini akan mengembalikan access_token dan refresh_token.
# Copy access_token ke variabel @token di bawah untuk menguji rute terproteksi admin.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/v1/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Accept: application/json

token_id=PUT_FIREBASE_GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 2. Refresh Access Token (Menggunakan Fitur Tim Anda)
# Kirim refresh_token untuk mendapatkan access_token yang baru.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/v1/refresh
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "PUT_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

###

# =========================================================================
# VARIABEL TOKEN UNTUK PENGUJIAN RUTE TERPROTEKSI (JWT)
# Tempel token akses hasil login/refresh di bawah ini tanpa tanda kutip:
# =========================================================================
@token = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_DI_SINI


### 3. Dapatkan Semua Informasi User Terpaginasi (Terproteksi JWT & AdminOnly)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/v1/users?status=all&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Dapatkan User yang Perlu Diverifikasi Terpaginasi (Terproteksi JWT & AdminOnly)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/v1/users?status=pending&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Dapatkan User yang Sudah Diverifikasi Terpaginasi (Terproteksi JWT & AdminOnly)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/v1/users?status=verified&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Lakukan Verifikasi - Setujui (Approve) Pendaftaran User (Terproteksi JWT & AdminOnly)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/v1/users/1/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "action": "approve"
}

###

### 7. Lakukan Verifikasi - Tolak (Reject) Pendaftaran User (Terproteksi JWT & AdminOnly)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/v1/users/1/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "action": "reject"
}

###

### 8. Ambil Struktur Pohon Referral Terstruktur (Terproteksi JWT & AdminOnly)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/v1/referrals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Ambil Ringkasan Dashboard Statistik Admin (Terproteksi JWT & AdminOnly)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/v1/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
